respawn_complex.name: Respawn Complex
respawn_complex.option.enable_activation: Respawn points need to be activated before they can be used.
respawn_complex.option.activate_method.t:
Activation method for respawn points:
  %s - Activate by interacting with the respawn point
  %s - Activate by interacting with block at the respawn point
  %s - Move to pos that close to the respawn point
respawn_complex.option.enable_sync.toolt: Respawn points will sync with blocks with tag #respawn_complex:respawn_point
